@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iiknpw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.69) + wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.21)))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.52)
    v1 = wp.exp((v2 - wp.exp(v1 + 0.33)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(tmp) / v2)
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
